i have one question. 
In Initial setup tacacs users are not in mongodb.
Tacacs user tries to login, the plugin will authenticate credentials with tacacs server. Assuming credentials are valid, they will be added to mongodb. However that user can't login since role project mapping is not yet done. So all tacacs users will Initially have a failed login and osm admin user will do project role mapping once this scenario is done. Mainly because tacacs don't have an api to fetch all users.
